    "work_description": "Holy Rosary Church and the Western Dominican Province have conducted an analysis of the density yield and design strategies for 4 properties under their control: Blocks 62, 67 68 & 211. A building to replace three (3) existing buildings of service to the parish and community: The Rosary Center; Siena Hall; and Aquinas Hall would be accommodated on Block 68. Block 62 would accommodate affordable housing, while Block 67 would accommodate market-rate housing. The interrelationship of the new buildings and the remainder of the Holy Rosary holdings have been modeled to show a Campus Master Plan.",
